BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 397.50 Td (Root cause:) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 372.50 Td (- AGX Thor defaults to 10GbE x4 mode on the QSFP/MGBE ports.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 360.00 Td (- The 25G FPGA design requires 25GbE x4.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 347.50 Td (- Thor does not support runtime switching between 10G and 25G using normal Linux network settings.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 335.00 Td (- nmcli, IP settings, Docker, and FPGA reprogramming alone cannot switch Thor to 25G.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 310.00 Td (5.2 25G Switching Method) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 281.50 Td (Altera provided capsule files for switching Thor bootloader/QSPI configuration between 10G and 25G.) Tj ET
