stream
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 725.50 Td (??????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 54 688.00 Td (9. Lessons Learned) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 643.00 Td (1. Thor default QSFP mode is 10G.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 630.50 Td (2. The 25G FPGA image will not link unless Thor is booted in 25G mode.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 618.00 Td (3. 10G/25G switching is not runtime-configurable using nmcli.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 605.50 Td (4. Capsule-based slot switching allows 10G/25G switching without wiping the Linux rootfs.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 593.00 Td (5. hololink-enumerate proves FPGA/HSB communication.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 580.50 Td (6. Camera I2C errors are separate from Ethernet link errors.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 568.00 Td (7. GUI/Holoviz failures are often X11 authorization problems, not camera/FPGA problems.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 555.50 Td (8. Always use Ctrl+C to stop apps, not Ctrl+Z.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 543.00 Td (9. .sof programming is volatile; reprogram FPGA after a board power cycle.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 530.50 Td (10. Record boot slot mapping before switching modes.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 493.00 Td (??????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 54 455.50 Td (10. Final Slot Mapping From This Bring-up) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 398.00 Td (slot 0 = 25G) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 387.50 Td (slot 1 = 10G) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 352.00 Td (Switch to 25G:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 314.50 Td (sudo nvbootctrl set-active-boot-slot 0) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 304.00 Td (sudo reboot) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.5 Tf 54 268.50 Td (Switch to 10G:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 231.00 Td (sudo nvbootctrl set-active-boot-slot 1) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 220.50 Td (sudo reboot) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
